                "citation-title": "Quaternion-capon beamformer using crossed-dipole arrays",
                "abstracts": "Adaptive beamforming using a crossed-dipole array is addressed in the hypercomplex framework. A new variant of Capon beamformer, called Quaternion-Capon (Q-Capon) beamformer, is herein proposed to fulfill the linearly constrained minimization operation in the quaternion domain. Simulation results show that the Q-Capon beamformer has a better convergence performance than the standard \"long-vector\" Capon beamformer, and is more robust than the latter to the uncertainty in signal's steering vector especially under the scenario of high signal to noise ratio values. © 2011 IEEE.",
